  "discoverGuideThreeBody": "Each day at 00:00 (Taipei time) we hand-pick 1–3 profiles (members always 3). Selection isn't random — we put people with shared interests, or who've thought about the same questions, in front of you.\n\nEveryone here passed review. Treat them the way you'd want to be treated.",
